            "answer": 0,
            "explain": "Yoneda: $\\mathrm{Nat}(h_X,F)\\cong F(X)$ naturally in $X$ and $F$. Evaluating at $\\mathrm{id}_X$ recovers the element, and any $x\\in F(X)$ determines the transformation $f\\mapsto F(f)(x)$."
