            "explain": "The pairing $\\langle f,g\\rangle=\\int fg\\,d\\mu$ is bounded by Hölder with constant $\\|g\\|_q$, and every bounded functional on $L^p$ arises this way — this is the content of the Riesz representation for $L^p$."
