            "explain": "Representability by $\\mathrm{Spec}\\,A$ means exactly that $F\\cong h_{\\mathrm{Spec}\\,A}$, i.e. $F(R)\\cong\\mathrm{Hom}(A,R)$ naturally in $R$. The universal element is the image of $\\mathrm{id}_A$."
