            "answer": 2,
            "explain": "A ring hom $\\mathbb{Z}[t,t^{-1}]\\to R$ is exactly a choice of unit of $R$ (the image of $t$ must be invertible). So $\\mathbb{G}_m=\\mathrm{Spec}\\,\\mathbb{Z}[t,t^{-1}]$."
