              "continuous homomorphism $\\rho:G_\\mathbb{Q}\\to\\mathrm{GL}_n(K)$ for $K\\in\\{\\mathbb{C},\\bar{\\mathbb{Q}}_\\ell,\\bar{\\mathbb{F}}_\\ell\\}$",
