            "answer": 3,
            "explain": "For $g\\ge 2$ the biholomorphism class varies in a $(6g-6)$-real-dimensional moduli space $\\mathcal{M}_g$; only topological/Hodge invariants like $\\chi,\\ b_1=2g,\\ \\dim H^0(\\Omega^1)=g$ are forced by $g$ alone."
