            "answer": 1,
            "explain": "The alternating Čech differential gives $(d t)_{\\alpha\\beta\\gamma}=t_{\\beta\\gamma}-t_{\\alpha\\gamma}+t_{\\alpha\\beta}$; setting it to zero is the cocycle condition on triple overlaps."
