            "tol": 0.000001,
            "explain": "$G(2)=4$: the excluded set $\\{4^a(8b+7)\\}$ is infinite, so even for large $n$ four squares are sometimes necessary. Hence $G(2)=g(2)=4$ is one of the rare cases with equality."
